---
title: Leek and Potato Filo Pie with Crunchy Honey Mustard Dressed Baby Gem
description: We love good Leek & Potato Filo Pie and this deliciously simple, chef-curated recipe doesn't disappoint. Time to bust out the pots and pans!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/leek-and-potato-filo-scrunch-pie-ed638bcd-5bf4289b.jpg
